    .hero-header
      h1.hero-heading Let's make<br> cool stuff
      picture.hero-avatar(width='155px', height='155px')
        source(srcset='/photo/avatar@2x.webp 2x, /photo/avatar.webp', type='image/webp')
        img.hero-avatar(src='/photo/avatar.jpg', srcset='/photo/avatar@2x.jpg 2x, /photo/avatar.jpg', alt='Mikhael Khrustik photo', itemprop='image')
    .hero-content
      p
        | Hi, my name is
        | #[span(itemprop='givenName') Mikhael]
        | #[span(itemprop='familyName') Khrustik],
        |  I'm a front lead and developer at
        | #[a(href='https://tektosoft.ru/') Tektosoft].
        | I live in St. Petersburg.
      p
        | Before that, I worked at #[a(href='https://belvg.com') BelVG],
        | #[a(href='https://cmtscience.ru/') CMT],
        | #[a(href='https://cifra.in/') Cifra] and
        | #[a(href='https://efo.ru/') EFO].
        | Was in charge of projects for #[a(href='https://latona.pro/') Latona],
        | #[a(href='https://web.archive.org/web/20180316073843/http://neochemicals.ru/') Neochemicals]
