      p
        | Drawing design, do layout, automating everything.
        | I like to take on difficult tasks that others would prefer to abandon.
      p.hero-footer
        | More information in #[a(href='/en/resume.pug') resume]. <br>
        | Write offers to the email:
        | #[a(href='mailto:misha@myrt.co', itemprop='email') misha@myrt.co], <br>
        | or Telegram: #[a(href='https://t.me/mishamyrt', itemprop='sameAs', rel='me') @mishamyrt]. <br>
        | Ещё я говорю #[a(href='/ru/index.pug') на русском языке].
      include ../hero/icons.pug
